a sign on the gates of
the concentration camp:

72
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:09,992
"Everyone gets what one deserves".

73
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:16,077
Attention! Caps on! Caps off!

74
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,871
Attention!

75
