- A seaside resort, pine trees.

78
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,916
Hello, Lithuanians.

79
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,950
We knew you're coming.

80
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,956
We've been waiting.

81
