Of what use are you to the Third Reich?

128
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:30,029
What can you do?

129
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:34,876
I can write poems.

130
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,991
I can write plays.

131
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,069
