You're the Professor?

235
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,916
Franz Bloy. From Cologne.

236
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,916
A thief. The green triangle.

237
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,871
Do you want to eat?

238
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:04,876
