Three years ago.

852
01:09:59,560 --> 01:10:01,516
Three years.

853
01:10:01,560 --> 01:10:03,551
To Wacek's health!

854
01:10:21,400 --> 01:10:22,549
And, Wacek,

855
01:10:24,600 --> 01:10:26,591
my wife wrote to me

856
