Cross out the entire chapter, if you want!

997
01:22:45,320 --> 01:22:49,279
But I won't let you cross out
separate sentences! Understand?

998
01:22:50,240 --> 01:22:51,434
Fucking asshole.

999
01:22:52,440 --> 01:22:54,237
Shit.

