1007
01:23:21,360 --> 01:23:23,430
You don't have to get your hair cut

1008
01:23:24,240 --> 01:23:25,434
as required in prison.

1009
01:23:26,240 --> 01:23:27,468
If it's still growing!

1010
01:23:29,280 --> 01:23:30,429
From now on

